# Markdown
## Links
Example:
Search for it: [Visit GitHub!][link]
[link]: www.github.com

## Paragraphs
A soft break, you can accomplist this by inserting two spaces after each new line. 
Example: 
Olala, Olalala  
Obaby, Obabyoo  
Yahhooo  

## Code
Example: 
```sh
print("Hello world!")
console.log("Damn")
cout << "Hola";
```
You want to run code C++, command `g++ code.cpp`
